        * <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25359703/" class="enlace-ref" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Joyal CC, Cossette A, Lapierre V. (2015). «What Exactly Is an Unusual Sexual Fantasy?»
        <em>Journal of Sexual Medicine</em>, 12(2):328–340.</a> Muestra: 1.516 adultos de población general.
